QUESTION NO: 1
What is NOT a recommendation when designing an archiving project?
A. archive business objects in their complete context
B. archive data through its full lifecycle
C. plan on retaining the archived data indefinitely
D. involve stakeholders to align business and legal requirements with the technology
Answer: C
QUESTION NO: 2
Which product is used to implement Optim Open Data Manager (ODM)?
A. Attunity Connect
B. Optim Directories
C. Export/Import Utility
D. MySQL
Answer: A
